 [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dassault_Mirage_2000\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dassault_Mirage_2000\"}, {\"begin\": 13692, \"end\": 13707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bombs\", \"from\": 13419, \"to\": 13424}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 13460, \"to\": 13469}, {\"ngram\": \"radar-surveillance planes\", \"from\": 13486, \"to\": 13511}, {\"ngram\": \"Reaper drones\", \"from\": 13516, \"to\": 13529}, {\"ngram\": \"sensitive sites\", \"from\": 13543, \"to\": 13558}, {\"ngram\": \"standby\", \"from\": 13611, \"to\": 13618}, {\"ngram\": \"aircraft\", \"from\": 13632, \"to\": 13640}, {\"ngram\": \"restricted airspace\", \"from\": 13655, \"to\": 13674}, {\"ngram\": \"a second mandate\", \"from\": 13717, \"to\": 13733}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 13759, \"to\": 13771}, {\"ngram\": \"his legacy\", \"from\": 13785, \"to\": 13795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But his failed bet on a snap legislative election has weakened him and cast a shadow over his moment on the international stage.More than 10,500 athletes will compete at the Olympics, 100 years since Paris last staged the Games.\", \"from\": 13797, \"to\": 14025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13997, \"end\": 14002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.271836311423489e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his failed bet\", \"from\": 13801, \"to\": 13815}, {\"ngram\": \"a snap legislative election\", \"from\": 13819, \"to\": 13846}, {\"ngram\": \"a shadow\", \"from\": 13873, \"to\": 13881}, {\"ngram\": \"his moment\", \"from\": 13887, \"to\": 13897}, {\"ngram\": \"the international stage\", \"from\": 13901, \"to\": 13924}, {\"ngram\": \"More than 10,500 athletes\", \"from\": 13925, \"to\": 13950}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 13967, \"to\": 13979}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 14015, \"to\": 14024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Competition started on Wednesday and the first of the 329 gold medals will be awarded on Saturday.\", \"from\": 14026, \"to\": 14124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Competition\", \"from\": 14026, \"to\": 14037}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 14049, \"to\": 14058}, {\"ngram\": \"the 329 gold medals\", \"from\": 14076, \"to\": 14095}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 14115, \"to\": 14123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The closing ceremony will take place on August 11.00votesArticle Rating Fountains threw up jets of water in the middle of the Seine as the boats went by, with athletes waving at the crowds, amid a huge visible police presence.\", \"from\": 14125, \"to\": 14352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14252, \"end\": 14257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999998640305, \"rank\": 1.0026725598834522e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The closing ceremony\", \"from\": 14125, \"to\": 14145}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 14156, \"to\": 14161}, {\"ngram\": \"August 11.00votesArticle\", \"from\": 14165, \"to\": 14189}, {\"ngram\": \"Rating Fountains\", \"from\": 14190, \"to\": 14206}, {\"ngram\": \"jets\", \"from\": 14216, \"to\": 14220}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 14224, \"to\": 14229}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 14233, \"to\": 14243}, {\"ngram\": \"the boats\", \"from\": 14260, \"to\": 14269}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 14284, \"to\": 14292}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 14303, \"to\": 14313}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge visible police presence\", \"from\": 14320, \"to\": 14350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony comes just hours after a sabotage attack on the high-speed TGV rail network caused travel chaos across France and put the spotlight on the security risks at a time when the eyes of the world are on the country.The show started by depicting a fictional scenario in which the arrival of the Olympic flame went awry, ahead of the extravagant show on the river to kick off the Summer Games.French soccer superstar Zinedine Zidane was shown running across Paris to bring the flame, in a pre-recorded video that included him taking it onto the metro.Spectators were treated to more postcard-like depictions of France as a huge cancan line performed by Moulin Rouge cabaret dancers on the banks.\", \"from\": 14354, \"to\": 15055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14426, \"end\": 14429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TGV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\"}, {\"begin\": 14470, \"end\": 14476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8223565367161532, \"rank\": 0.21601206339955795, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 14777, \"end\": 14792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zinedine_Zidane\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zinedine Zidane\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zinedine_Zidane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zinedine_Zidane\"}, {\"begin\": 14818, \"end\": 14823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.271836311423489e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 14971, \"end\": 14977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8223565367161532, \"rank\": 0.21601206339955795, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 15013, \"end\": 15025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.653064933950572e-22, \"text\": \"Moulin Rouge\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ceremony\", \"from\": 14354, \"to\": 14366}, {\"ngram\": \"a sabotage attack\", \"from\": 14390, \"to\": 14407}, {\"ngram\": \"travel chaos\", \"from\": 14450, \"to\": 14462}, {\"ngram\": \"the spotlight\", \"from\": 14485, \"to\": 14498}, {\"ngram\": \"the security risks\", \"from\": 14502, \"to\": 14520}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 14524, \"to\": 14530}, {\"ngram\": \"the eyes\", \"from\": 14536, \"to\": 14544}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 14548, \"to\": 14557}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 14565, \"to\": 14576}, {\"ngram\": \"The show\", \"from\": 14577, \"to\": 14585}, {\"ngram\": \"a fictional scenario\", \"from\": 14607, \"to\": 14627}, {\"ngram\": \"the arrival\", \"from\": 14637, \"to\": 14648}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic flame\", \"from\": 14652, \"to\": 14669}, {\"ngram\": \"the extravagant show\", \"from\": 14690, \"to\": 14710}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 14714, \"to\": 14723}, {\"ngram\": \"the Summer Games\", \"from\": 14736, \"to\": 14752}, {\"ngram\": \"French soccer superstar\", \"from\": 14753, \"to\": 14776}, {\"ngram\": \"the flame\", \"from\": 14833, \"to\": 14842}, {\"ngram\": \"a pre-recorded video\", \"from\": 14847, \"to\": 14867}, {\"ngram\": \"the metro\", \"from\": 14901, \"to\": 14910}, {\"ngram\": \"Spectators\", \"from\": 14911, \"to\": 14921}, {\"ngram\": \"more postcard-like depictions\", \"from\": 14938, \"to\": 14967}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge cancan line\", \"from\": 14981, \"to\": 14999}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 15045, \"to\": 15054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are super excited, it happens once in a lifetime,\\\" 17-year-old Elise Boukorrass said before the show.AYA NAKAMURA SINGSA more modern image of France was on display when French-Malian singer Aya Nakamura sang some of her biggest hits, as well as one by beloved crooner Charles Aznavour, accompanied by the French army choir.Nakamura's performance drew some of the biggest cheers so far from those by the river and watching the ceremony in bars.She is the most-listened-to French female singer in the world but when it first emerged she might perform it sparked a row over French identity.\", \"from\": 15055, \"to\": 15646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15201, \"end\": 15207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995073740262935, \"rank\": 0.0004915505902505328, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 15249, \"end\": 15261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aya_Nakamura\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aya Nakamura\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aya_Nakamura\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aya_Nakamura\"}, {\"begin\": 15327, \"end\": 15343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Aznavour\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charles Aznavour\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Aznavour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Aznavour\"}, {\"begin\": 15364, \"end\": 15370, \"title\": \"http://