r - their face hidden and identity concealed - was shown jumping on the roofs of Paris.The two most decorated athletes in the Games' history, Michael Phelps and Martin Fourcade, unveiled the gold, silver and bronze medals.SECURITY OPERATIONSome 45,000 police and thousands of soldiers have been deployed in a huge security operation in Paris for the opening show.\", \"from\": 51559, \"to\": 51936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 51715, \"end\": 51729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.653867389378428e-20, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 51734, \"end\": 51749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Fourcade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Martin Fourcade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Fourcade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Fourcade\"}, {\"begin\": 51909, \"end\": 51914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999973171043, \"rank\": 2.682872618341574e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The torchbearer\", \"from\": 51559, \"to\": 51574}, {\"ngram\": \"their face\", \"from\": 51577, \"to\": 51587}, {\"ngram\": \"the roofs\", \"from\": 51641, \"to\": 51650}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 51654, \"to\": 51659}, {\"ngram\": \"The two most decorated athletes\", \"from\": 51660, \"to\": 51691}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games' history\", \"from\": 51695, \"to\": 51713}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold, silver and bronze medals\", \"from\": 51760, \"to\": 51794}, {\"ngram\": \"45,000 police\", \"from\": 51818, \"to\": 51831}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 51836, \"to\": 51845}, {\"n